data.text:
Timbaland is an American record producer, songwriter and rapper.

His first full credit production work was in 1996 for R&B singer Ginuwine. He would workk on Aaliyah's 1996 album One in a Million and Missy Elliott's 1997 album Supa Dupa Fly.

He released his debut solo album Tim's Bio in 1998. In 2005 Timbaland released the first album in his Shock Value series, Timbaland Presents: Shock Value followed by Timbaland Presents: Shock Value II in 2009 and Timbaland Presents: Shock Value III in 2012.
